<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <head xml:lang="en">Commentary</head>
      <p xml:id="TNV6comm1">e-tu. karupporuḷ ām āṟuṇarttutaṉutaliṟṟu.</p>
      <p xml:id="TNV6comm2">collappaṭṭa mutaṟporuṭkuriya teyvamum avvaḻi vāḻumakkaḷum 
      avarkaḷ toḻilkaḷum uṇpārkkut tuppākiya uṇavum icaiyum āṅkaṇ vāḻum vilaṅkukaḷum 
      piṟavum aintiṇaikkup peṟṟa karupporuḷā meṉṟavāṟu. <note>(6)</note></p>
      </body>
